{"word":"Amariah","slug":"amariah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Amariah</b> <a href=\"#/H568\">H568</a> <br/> 1. Two Levites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=7'>1Ch 6:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=52'>1Ch 6:52</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=19'>1Ch 23:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=24&verse=23'>1Ch 24:23</a><br/> 2. Chief priest in the reign of Jehoshaphat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=19&verse=11'>2Ch 19:11</a><br/> 3. A high priest, father of Ahitub<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=11'>1Ch 6:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=3'>Ezr 7:3</a><br/> 4. A Levite, who assisted in distributing temple gifts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=31&verse=19'>2Ch 31:19</a><br/> 5. Son of Hizkiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=1&verse=1'>Zep 1:1</a><br/> 6. Father of Zechariah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=4'>Neh 11:4</a><br/> 7. A priest, returned from exile<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=3'>Neh 10:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=2'>Neh 12:2</a> <br/> - Probably identical with one mentioned in Nehemia 12:13<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=13'>Neh 12:13</a> <br/> 8. A returned exile. Divorces his idolatrous wife<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=42'>Ezr 10:42</a>"}]}